{"tid":1781361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國大選保守黨奪過半數議席　約翰遜：強力新民意授權脫歐","createTime":"2019-12-13T05:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T07:30:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c47f907bea83e7c59dd4630a85b154bfd2f668ab","tid":1781361,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497481-20191213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497481-20191213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=09c7b34d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497481-20191213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=edc5d07f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497481-20191213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國大選陸續公布官方結果，執政保守黨已經贏得國會下議院過半數議席，有利通過脫歐協議，保守黨暫時奪得326個議席，在野工黨得196席。<br />\n<br />\n領導保守黨的約翰遜在所屬選區勝出，他感謝參與投票的選民，形容是強力的新民意授權，希望能落實脫歐。<br />\n<br />\n在野工黨失去多個議席，黨魁郝爾賓雖然在所屬選區勝出，但他宣布，不會再帶領工黨參與下次選舉。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，脫歐議題影響選民意向和對黨派的忠誠度，令其他黨派的選民轉投保守黨。"},{"pid":"2fb78f4b3f3193fb6937d7fcd10156673cc50a31","tid":1781361,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"當日MAY姐仲做緊PM時<br />\n<br />\n一堆大一統兒登仔係度鳩叫「約翰遜唔係搞脫歐公投咩？去咗邊呀？去咗邊呀」<br />\n<br />\n呢堆大一統兒登仔, 依家縮返去老母閪度<br />\n<br />\n所以話, 港豬政治低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664b65de0a711ceb4b22f3574c2cab4300918ff3","tid":1781361,"uid":60655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"終於脫得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621a5df01641874ea38207bca9e76d66ec9933e1","tid":1781361,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:01